Package com.landawn.abacus.util

Class Splitter.MapSplitter

java.lang.Object
com.landawn.abacus.util.Splitter.MapSplitter
Enclosing class:
Splitter
public static final class Splitter.MapSplitter extends Object
This is the MapSplitter class. It provides various methods to split a string into a map based on different criteria. The class supports splitting by character, CharSequence, and Pattern. It also provides options to control the splitting behavior, such as whether to omit empty strings, whether to trim results, and whether to limit the number of substrings. The class also includes methods for splitting strings into maps with specific key and value types.
